Implementation experience with ITSM, Customer Service Management and PPS - Project Portfolio Suite, configuration of Idea, Demand Management, Project Management, Project templates, Portfolios, Agile development, SDLC, Resource Management, Test Management, Performance Analytics & ServicePortal.
